    <txt_Content><![CDATA[<table width="100%">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 20px;" valign="top">
                    <p><strong>歡迎來到冬季的澳洲。</strong></p>
                    <p>對於澳洲國內大部分的地區而言，冬季從6月持續到8月；至於在熱帶氣候的北部地區，這幾個月是較乾旱的季節。在維多利亞州鋪滿粉雪的山坡上進行雪橇或雪板滑雪，或是到昆士蘭州大堡礁溫和的水域中浮潛或潛水。駕駛四驅車探索南澳州的辛普森沙漠（Simpson Desert），或是去藍山參加各式各樣的聖誕慶祝活動。觀賞西澳州野花路徑上的美景，或是體驗北領地獨特的節日文化。在坎培拉爐邊節上蜷伏在熊熊爐火邊鬆弛身心，或是在荷伯特鋪滿鵝卵石的街道上慶祝冬至的到來。冬天還是探索我們的海岸線的大好時節，您可以在那裡觀察遷徙的鯨魚，並潛水進入多姿多彩的海洋世界。</p>
                    <br />
                    <p><img alt="這裡的冬季將您帶到" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-zht-title01.jpg" /></p>
                    <table width="100%">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/qld/qld-winter-sun.xml" target="_self"><img alt="北部昆士蘭的冬日陽光" src="/contentimages/explore-states-qld-winter-sun-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/qld/qld-winter-sun.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">北部昆士蘭的冬日陽光</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><strong><span style="color: #dd8905; font-size: 12px;"></span></strong><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>今年冬天來北部昆士蘭度假，享受溫和的氣候和搖曳的棕櫚，在宜人的海中暢游，令朋友們羨慕不已。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/vic/vic-snow-play.xml" target="_self"><img alt="在維多利亞州山區嬉雪" src="/contentimages/explore-states-vic-snow-play-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/vic/vic-snow-play.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">在維多利亞州山區嬉雪</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>不能想像澳洲有積雪覆蓋的高山？冬天在維多利亞州，您能在十個一流的山區雪場找到幾百條滑雪道。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/wa/wa-wildflowers.xml" target="_self"><img alt="西部野花" src="/contentimages/explore-states-wa-wildflowers-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/wa/wa-wildflowers.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">西部野花</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>將單調的日子和荒涼的地貌拋諸腦後。從六月到九月，全州各地會有12000多種野花盛開綻放。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/sa/sa-desert-adventure.xml" target="_self"><img alt="南澳州的沙漠探險" src="/contentimages/explore-states-sa-winter-desert-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/sa/sa-desert-adventure.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">南澳州的沙漠探險</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>今年冬天給自己一個挑戰，駕駛四驅車探索廣袤而永恒的辛普森沙漠（Simpson Desert）在南澳境內的部分。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/tas/tas-winter-secrets.xml" target="_self"><img alt="塔斯曼尼亞冬天的秘密" src="/contentimages/explore-states-tas-winter-secrets-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/tas/tas-winter-secrets.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">塔斯曼尼亞冬天的秘密</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>在荷伯特（Hobart）慶祝冬至，或者到本洛蒙德國家公園（Ben Lomond National Park）滑雪。到搖籃山（Cradle Mountain）白雪覆蓋的高原上遠足，或是在酒杯灣（Wineglass Bay）的旅舍舒服地蜷伏在火爐邊。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/nt/nt-festival-fun.xml" target="_self"><img alt="旱季的節日狂歡" src="/contentimages/explore-states-nt-festival-fun-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/states/nt/nt-festival-fun.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">旱季的節日狂歡</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>在澳洲北領地，五月到十月的旱季是到戶外慶祝的最佳時節。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/cities/sydney/nsw-bluemts-yulefest.xml" target="_self"><img alt="藍山的七月聖誕" src="/contentimages/explore-cities-sydney-blue-mountains-yulefest-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/cities/sydney/nsw-bluemts-yulefest.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">藍山的七月聖誕</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>每年六月到八月，成千上萬人會涌到藍山參加聖誕節慶活動——熊熊爐火、燒烤大餐、放聲高歌，偶爾還有白雪飄飄。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/cities/canberra/act-fireside-festival.xml" target="_self"><img alt="坎培拉爐火邊的溫暖" src="/contentimages/explore-cities-canberra-fireside-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/cities/canberra/act-fireside-festival.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #82af54; font-size: 12px;">坎培拉爐火邊的溫暖</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/horizontal-line-short-grey.JPG" /></p>
                                <p>每年八月坎培拉地區都會舉辦爐邊節（Fireside Festival），來感受熊熊爐火邊的暖意，享用豐盛的美食。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                    <p style="padding-bottom: 15px;"><img alt="旅程" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-zht-title02.jpg" /></p>
                    <p><img alt="比布蒙路徑, 西澳州" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-hl01.jpg" /></p>
                    <table width="100%">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding-right: 5px;" valign="top" colspan="2">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/itineraries-ideas/walking-australia.xml" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: #608eab; font-size: 12px;">澳洲的步行路徑</span></strong></a></p>
                                <p>在澳洲眾多令人難忘的步行路徑上展開腿腳、擴闊心靈，觀賞眾多獨特的地貌。走走一日行路徑、較短的風景路段，或是征服從頭到尾需幾個星期甚至幾個月才能走完的旅程。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width: 42%; padding-right: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/nt-larapinta-trail.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">拉拉平塔路徑, 北領地</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/sa-heysen-trail.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">希臣徑, 南澳州</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/wa-bibbulmun-track.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">比布蒙路徑, 西澳州</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/vic-wilsons-prom.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">威爾遜岬, 維多利亞州</span></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td style="width: 58%;" valign="top">
                                <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/tas-overland-track.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">陸上路徑, 塔斯曼尼亞</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/nsw-six-foot-track.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">六英呎路徑, 新南威爾斯</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/qld-goldcoast-hinterland.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">黃金海岸腹地步行路徑</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" src="/contentimages/arrow-blue.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/act-australian-alps-walking-track.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;">澳洲高山區徒步路徑</span></a></p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <br />
                    <p style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><img alt="大草原之路" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-hl02.jpg" /></p>
                    <p><a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/qld-savannah-way.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #608eab;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>大草原之路 - 6天駕車游</strong></span></span></a></p>
                    <p>從凱恩斯出發，駕車穿過昆士蘭蔥郁的熱帶高地（Tropical Tablelands）和歷史悠久的金礦區，到達地處偏遠的薩瓦那灣（Gulf Savannah）與北領地（Northern Territory）邊界。</p>
                    <br />
                    <p><a href="/zht/explore/things-to-do/australian-adventure/nat-whalewatching.xml" target="_self"><img alt="觀鯨時節" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-zht-title03.jpg" /></a></p>
                    <table width="98%">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width: 50%; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/things-to-do/australian-adventure/nat-whalewatching.xml" target="_self"><img alt="觀鯨時節 " src="/contentimages/explore-things-to-see-do-adventure-whale-watching-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td style="width: 50%;" valign="top">
                                <p>每年冬天，觀看座頭鯨經過拜倫灣（Byron Bay）和哈維灣（Hervey Bay）向北遷徙。驚嘆於牠們利用複雜的特技進行交流的方式，透過水底聽音器聆聽雄性鯨魚令人難以忘記的水下歌聲。在地理灣（Geographe Bay）、登斯波若（Dunsborough）和阿伯尼（Albany）觀看行動緩慢優雅的南露脊鯨沿西澳州海岸線北上。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <br />
                    <p><a href="/zht/explore/things-to-do/australian-adventure/nat-diving.xml" target="_self"><img alt="潛水探索澳大利亞" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-winter-zht-title04.jpg" /></a></p>
                    <table width="98%">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width: 50%; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 5px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/things-to-do/australian-adventure/nat-diving.xml" target="_self"><img alt="潛水探索澳大利亞" src="/contentimages/explore-things-to-see-do-adventure-diving-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td style="width: 50%;" valign="top">
                                <p>澳大利亞完全被水環繞，擁有眾多的島嶼和珊瑚礁，是一個潛水者的天堂。我們的水域中棲息著大量珍貴的海洋生物，其中包括4000多種魚類和世界上種類最繁多的海草。在寧格魯礁（Ningaloo Reef）游到巨大而溫和的鯨鯊身邊，或是在南澳的艾爾半島（Eyre Peninsula）與海獅和海豚共游。</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
